title: UNIVERSAL MORALITY A Crossover with The Elucidations Podcast
itunes:author: Toby Buckle
itunes:summary: In this episode, I talk with Matt Teichman, host of the elucidations podcast.  We debate if there is such a thing as a universal morality that's common to all cultures, and what we learn from the diversity of moral and political thought in history.
